high_descs: Turn to the right and the right again to stand at the end of the counter.
Pick up the potato from the back side of the counter.
Carry the potato and go straight ahead to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the potato inside. Shut the door, then open it again and take the potato out. Shut the door.
Carry the potato and turn around to locate the stove.
Place the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Chill and then heat a potato.

high_descs: Walk passed the refrigerator to the end of the counter.
Pick up the potato from the counter.
Take the potato to the refrigerator.
Put the potato on the bottom shelf of the refrigerator, close the doors, wait a few seconds, and then open and remove, then close the fridge.
Take the potato to the stove.
Put the potato in the microwave above the stove.
anns.task_desc: Chill a potato in the refrigerator, prepare cook it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, go toward the fridge, then turn right and go forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the potato on the counter.
Turn right, go forward, then turn right to go to the fridge.
Chill the potato in the fridge.
Turn around, go straight, then turn left to go to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato in the microwave.
